1420
01:07:07.762 --> 01:07:09.029
Taylor drowned.

1421
01:07:10.230 --> 01:07:11.966
He went to Princeton
on a swimming scholarship

1422
01:07:12.065 --> 01:07:13.500
and he drowned.

1423
01:07:14.802 --> 01:07:17.337
I became more than a bit
suspicious right then.

1424
01:07:18.272 --> 01:07:20.340
So I had a little friend
follow you.

1425
01:07:21.609 --> 01:07:23.076
Aren't those great?

1426
01:07:24.444 --> 01:07:26.146
I'm really happy
