1433
01:07:47.234 --> 01:07:48.302
It's almost as if.
I don't know.

1434
01:07:48.402 --> 01:07:49.704
they don't quite have a case.

1435
01:07:51.238 --> 01:07:53.140
Which is bananas.

1436
01:07:55.577 --> 01:07:58.412
