checkbook. right?

1443
01:08:09.423 --> 01:08:11.693
You still have access
to the accounts?

1444
01:08:12.627 --> 01:08:14.127
Deliver the cheques
to my husband.

1445
01:08:14.227 --> 01:08:16.030
