1451
01:08:24.338 --> 01:08:27.075
Your little girlfriend.
who do you think?

1452
01:08:27.174 --> 01:08:29.677
Cardozo High School
in Bayside. Queens. right?

1453
01:08:31.178 --> 01:08:32.680
