1487
01:10:12.880 --> 01:10:15.817
But you... you're really
coming up in the world. huh?

1488
01:10:18.619 --> 01:10:21.321
Just... Just a little bastard.

1489
01:10:21.421 --> 01:10:23.725
Just a little bastard
from Newark. (CHUCKLES)

