-(SHELL CLATTERING)

1570
01:17:04.692 --> 01:17:05.860
Here.

1571
01:17:06.327 --> 01:17:07.628
Go ahead.

1572
01:17:09.230 --> 01:17:10.197
Go ahead.

1573
01:17:13.367 --> 01:17:15.102
