talk to you. okay?

1636
01:21:55.517 --> 01:21:57.886
All right. All right. Um...
(CLEARS THROAT)

1637
01:21:57.985 --> 01:21:59.253
I... I need to... I need to go

1638
01:21:59.353 --> 01:22:01.221
'cause I have
my engagement party.

1639
01:22:02.089 --> 01:22:03.123
<i>It started an hour ago.</i>

1640
01:22:03.223 --> 01:22:04.425
OFFICER:
<i>Whose engagement party?</i>

1641
01:22:04.526 --> 01:22:05.392
BECKET: <i>It's mine.</i>

1642
01:22:05.492 --> 01:22:07.394
DETECTIVE: So you had
no relationship

1643
01:22:07.494 --> 01:22:08.663
with your grandfather?

1644
01:22:08.763 --> 01:22:10.931
I'd never met him
before tonight.

1645
01:22:11.031 --> 01:22:14.001
-Not even once?
-BECKET: Never.

1646
01:22:14.101 --> 01:22:15.936
Look. if I'm not
legally required to be here.

1647
01:22:16.036 --> 01:22:17.705
I need to leave.

1648
01:22:17.806 --> 01:22:19.072
You're not
legally required to.

1649
01:22:19.173 --> 01:22:21.175
but. uh...
I'd prefer if you stay.

1650
01:22:21.275 --> 01:22:22.242
Okay.

